22 Transportation is informed and believes may have or claim to have an interest
23 in said lands, the land, so far as the same can by reasonable diligence be
24 ascertained and if any such can be ascertained by reasonable diligence. The
25 Department shall state whether any persons are infants, non compos mentis,
26 or under any other disability, or their whereabouts or names unknown, it must
